text: chaur anak( mou ham meat) sautr nouv avei delke ban phdal vea hi aoy anak nei kompir( kuor an) haey chaur anak brate b tde sa la t . pitabrakd nasa sa la t ach hamkhat ampi kar br pru td aseilothmr ning ampeutouchcharit . haey kar romluk tow champoh a l laoh ku pitchea thomtheng bamphot . haey a l laoh doeng nouv avei del puok anak br pru td
